<plot>Lucifer, God's most beautiful angel. Lucifer was the prince of angels, the bearer of light. He placed his own beauty and perfection above his love for God. This sin of pride caused his fall to the darkest domain where, known as Satan, he struggles as God's rival. This film poetically explores the Lucifer tale as manifested in man's realm.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?346493</url></doc>
